#. TRANSLATION: shared
msgctxt "game_options"
msgid ""
"Adjust the cpu power frequency profile whilst in-game. Some systems will "
"benefit from improved voltage handling."
msgstr ""
"ゲーム中に CPU電力周波数プロファイルを調整します。 一部のシステムでは、電圧処"
"理の改善によるメリットが得られます"

#. TRANSLATION: shared
msgctxt "game_options"
msgid "POWER OPTIONS"
msgstr "電源オプション"

#. TRANSLATION: shared
msgctxt "game_options"
msgid "POWER MODE"
msgstr "パワーモード"

#. TRANSLATION: shared
msgctxt "game_options"
msgid "High Performance"
msgstr "ハイパフォーマンス"

#. TRANSLATION: shared
msgctxt "game_options"
msgid "Balanced"
msgstr "バランス"

#. TRANSLATION: shared
msgctxt "game_options"
msgid "Power Saver"
msgstr "パワーセーバー"

#. TRANSLATION: shared
msgctxt "game_options"
msgid ""
"Adjust the cpu power profile whist on battery. Overwrites previous Power "
"Mode(s)."
msgstr ""
"バッテリーを使用しながら CPU電力プロファイルを調整します。 以前の電力モードを"
"上書きします"

#. TRANSLATION: shared
msgctxt "game_options"
msgid "BATTERY MODE"
msgstr "バッテリーモード"

#. TRANSLATION: shared
msgctxt "game_options"
msgid ""
"Adjust the percentage of power (watts) provided to a Ryzen Mobile Series CPU "
"based on it's default max value. Caution, setting wattage too high could "
"damage your device."
msgstr ""
"Ryzen Mobile シリーズ CPU に提供される電力 (ワット) の割合を調整します\n"
"設定が高すぎるとデバイスが損傷する可能性があります"

#. TRANSLATION: shared
msgctxt "game_options"
msgid "RYZEN THERMAL DESIGN POWER"
msgstr "RYZEN 熱設計電力"

#. TRANSLATION: shared
msgctxt "game_options"
msgid "Set the display's resolution. Does not affect the rendering resolution."
msgstr "ディスプレイ解像度を設定(レンダリング解像度には影響しません)"

#. TRANSLATION: mame, shared
msgctxt "game_options"
msgid "VIDEO MODE"
msgstr "ゲーム画面モード"

#. TRANSLATION: pcsx2, shared
msgctxt "game_options"
msgid ""
"Force the game to render in this aspect ratio. Not all systems support all "
"ratios."
msgstr "ゲームの表示アスペクト比を設定(未対応の比率もあります)"

#. TRANSLATION: dolphin, flycast, mupen64plus, pcsx2, shared
msgctxt "game_options"
msgid "GAME ASPECT RATIO"
msgstr "ゲーム画面比率"

#. TRANSLATION: libretro/hatarib, libretro/pcsx2, openmohaa, shared
msgctxt "game_options"
msgid "Full"
msgstr "フルモード"

